name: Rachel-Rose O'Leary
description: Rachel-Rose O'Leary is a DarkFi core developer and writer. She authored 'Lunarpunk and the Dark Side of the Cycle', a text which helped create a web3 privacy revival. She is the lead editor of the philosophy journal Agorism in the 21st Century. She was the tech lead for CoinDesk 2017-2018, and has written for WIRED, Rekt News and Defiant. She has a background in philosophy and digital art.
